Subject: Aftercare Variations and Negotiations
Description: Who needs aftercare? Is it only needed after hardcore sessions? Is all aftercare the same? What are some options for negotiating aftercare? What aftercare have you given/received that seemed to work well? What aftercare obstacles have you encountered, and what are some ideas for coping with them? How are aftercare, safety, and consent related? Lets talk. This event is 18+.  Speakers include:Sarah - Track: After Dark  - Duration: 1 hour
